Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=16}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos chegando na saída.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Descendo direto, a todo vapor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:01.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:02.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Quêêê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:27.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza, o Sea Train emergiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos, pessoal! Nós também vamos lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pulem, Sodom e Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sr. Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:48.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Em nome de toda a Família Franky,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:52.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q\an8}obrigado por nos levarem junto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Disparem os canhões de conexão!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses são king bulls de primeira linha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nada mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:18.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Aqueles malditos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, imbecis, cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Obrigado pela ajuda!\N– Obrigado pela ajuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que os trilhos desviaram bastante.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:31.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eu acompanhei o Sea Train\Ndesde o primeiro dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:33.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me subestimem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:38.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estou vendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mensagem urgente da sala de máquinas!
Comment: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The train will get on the railway shortly.
Comment: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once it does, it'll rapidly accelerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:50.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Em instantes, o trem vai entrar nos trilhos\Ne acelerar rapidamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:54.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Segurem-se firme se quiserem\Nminimizar os ferimentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vamos nos machucar de qualquer jeito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Comportem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vovó, essa foi muito por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um pouco pra direita!
Comment: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:12.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É só esperar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou conseguir na próx–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chimney! Gonbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês duas se esconderam a bordo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, escondemos!
Comment: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo amor de Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rápido, entrem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão ser levadas pelo vento!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos bem! Estamos bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:41.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou cair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:48.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Não solte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou ser levada pelo vento!
Comment: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:51.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:53.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Espere um pouco, tá?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou parar o trem agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O freio não funciona neste trem!
Comment: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Woah! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é isso? Parece até divertido.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o cara do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Comment: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha! Rápido, coloque\Na Chimney e o Gonbe pra dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando entrarmos nos trilhos,\Neles vão ser levados pelo vento!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:24.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Pensei que ia morrer.\N– Pensei que ia morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obviamente! Meu Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu avisei, não avisei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que vocês iam ser levados pelo vento!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, ai, ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela aceleração foi de louco.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:14.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Francamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, sério, que susto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bati a lombar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere um pouco...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temos uma companhia inesperada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?! Quem são eles?!\N– O quê?! Quem são eles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele está falando de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso inclui vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por mais que eu tentasse\Nparar vocês, continuavam vindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O inimigo do qual vocês fariam de tudo\Npara resgatar seu amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:41.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é o mesmo que tentou matar o Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:45.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E eu tenho umas palavras pra eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie! Não vamos deixar\Nvocê ficar com toda a glória!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:53.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Achamos que encontraríamos os assassinos\Ndo Sr. Iceburg se seguíssemos vocês,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,então nos escondemos no vagão de carvão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:58.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E... parece que estávamos certos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixem a gente entrar nessa batalha com vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E o inimigo de vocês é, claro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,os mesmos malditos que levaram o Mano Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:10.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso aí, e sabemos\Nexatamente quem são!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:14.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E aí, Galley-La, como vão resolver\Nse não trazemos nosso Mano de volta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Calem a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:18.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Sr. Iceburg quem mais sofreu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do que vocês estão falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Paulie, nos coloque a par! O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem razão, Paulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:28.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você sabe quem é o verdadeiro culpado, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só diga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:32.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não somos tão burros assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já temos uma ideia de quem é.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vamos ficar surpresos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:42.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, provavelmente ficou óbvio\Nquando eles sumiram de repente.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vou falar direto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As verdadeiras identidades daqueles homens mascarados são...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:52.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci, Kaku, Kalifa e Blueno do bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:57.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eles{\i0} tentaram matar o Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Não era óbvio pra vocês?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,M-Mas você disse que eles voltaram pra casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Numa hora dessas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:08.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente achou que era o Michael\Ne o Hoichael dos Becos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:08.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, é!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:09.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem e {\i1}quem{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Quê?! Vocês não conhecem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são famosos nos Becos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, é!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu ia saber?! Vocês são–
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:17.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cara, comi muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente estou satisfeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Família Franky! Carpinteiros da Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:35.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Podemos ter tido nossos problemas na cidade,\Nmas agora estamos todos atrás do mesmo inimigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:40.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele idiota do pombo vai ser\No cara mais forte que vamos enfrentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:43.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é meu. Vou acabar com ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:48.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esta é uma batalha pra recuperar\No que aqueles quatro tiraram de nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:52.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, não vamos conseguir\Nfazer nada sem alcançá-los.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:57.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vovó! Vovó! É a Aqua Laguna!
Comment: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:57.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah? Já chegou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chimney, deixa eu ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:11.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sra. Kokoro, você não deveria\Nestar na sala de máquinas agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Precisamos desviar daquela onda enorme de algum jeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não avisei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não conseguimos controlar o {\i1}Rocketman{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que tentássemos operá-lo,\Nnada funciona, incluindo o freio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu trabalho acabou quando o trem\Nentrou nos trilhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Este trem sempre vai a toda velocidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ninguém mais pode pará-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Comment: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If we don't do anything, the train will crash into the big wave!
Comment: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faça alguma coisa, ou vamos bater\Nnaquela onda enorme! Ei, Luffy–
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se temos o mesmo objetivo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,seria burrice lutar separados.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entenderam? Somos companheiros.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos os nossos amigos...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:58.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,estão naquele trem ali na frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só vamos ganhar mais aliados!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:04.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vamos deixar uma onda nos derrubar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos nós vamos alcançar nosso objetivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mostrem o que podem fazer contra essa onda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Disparem todas as balas de canhão\Nque temos contra aquela onda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando se trata de canhões, deixem comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:30.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Família Franky! Firmes contra aquela onda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:31.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preparem os canhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Entendido!\N– Entendido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mexam-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Den Den Mushi portátil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, Capitão T-Bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com seu braço?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:19.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,F-Fui picado por um inseto antes.\NQuando cocei, sangrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que terrível! Precisamos estancar\No sangramento imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos usar isto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sua própria capa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:31.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pronto, isso deve resolver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:36.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando meus subordinados sangram,\Né meu coração que se machuca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão T-Bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:46.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Que o mundo seja pacífico\Ne gentil novamente hoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.40,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,– A cara dele é super assustadora.\N– A cara dele é super assustadora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:53.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eu... não disse nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:04.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se é algo que eu posso fazer, farei,\Nmesmo que meu corpo seja destruído.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:11.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os oficiais nos vagões seis e sete\Nforam eliminados.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:17.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(5146,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Além disso, os dois criminosos detidos\Nno vagão seis também desapareceram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:23.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não conseguimos dizer se há um intruso\Nou se escaparam sozinhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como isso é possível?!
Comment: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Save the lives of the injured immediately,
Comment: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,and let everyone on this train know about this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:29.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cuidem dos feridos imediatamente\Ne alertem todos sobre a situação!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami, está me ouvindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sim! É você, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:40.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As coisas estão ficando feias aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ficando feias?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sanji! Quem está com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ei! O que está acontecendo?! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.79,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei, ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, graças a um certo idiota.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:54.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-Idiota?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! De novo! O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vocês estão bem, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quem é esse idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.34,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vocês estão bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.05,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Brincadeirinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.64,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mas vocês parecem agitados.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, são dois idiotas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Demi-Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Fogo!\N– Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nem estamos fazendo efeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é nenhuma surpresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Esses canhõezinhos não vão funcionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pessoal! Pra trás!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:28.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixem com o canhão especial da Família Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alvo! Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Super Scrap Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Firmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Continuem atirando!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.23,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(19,816,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Reabasteçam as balas de canhão!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:54.90,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.44,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Mirem na frente! Foco num ponto só!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai! Foco total!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Façam o melhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:07.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O trilho flutua um pouco,\Nmas não o suficiente pra passar sobre a Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:12.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se batermos de frente,\Nmesmo o {\i1}Rocketman{\i0} vira sucata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:15.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos morrer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu disse pra se prepararem, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Nós também?!
Comment: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:26.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então a Robin ainda...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Parece animado aí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Diz, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou te contar as razões da Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e nossa situação atual, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escuta, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:53.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou te contar tudo sobre o motivo\Ndas ações da Robin e nossa situação atual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ouça com atenção.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos bater!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não! Vamos morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Menos choro, mais tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.84,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Achem uma saída!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Continuem atirando na frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos disparar nosso próprio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,canhão.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto é 108 vezes 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É 216.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, 216...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é um bocado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, escolha qualquer número.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-O que eles estão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que podem fazer\Ncom punhos e espadas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles mandaram a gente continuar atirando.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chega de conversa! Deem cobertura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, então... 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:25.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Three-Hundred-Pound...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Vamos bater!\N– Vamos bater!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– ...Cannon!\N– ...Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:35.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– C-Conseguimos passar!\N– C-Conseguimos passar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:46.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Atravessamos a Aqua Laguna!\N– Atravessamos a Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei que íamos morrer!
Comment: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Comment: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ei! Vocês estão bem, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, de alguma forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquilo foi demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se chamam de piratas à toa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu odiaria ser inimigo deles,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:34.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas são aliados muito confiáveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:35.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Chapéu de Palha!\N– Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sinceramente, achei que estávamos mortos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que caras incríveis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não baixem a guarda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ainda não saímos da tempestade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem nada que nos assuste agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso foi divertido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha! Você é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:02.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele foi um poder sobre-humano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, venha aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É o Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, é você, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Como estão as coisas aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:22.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cadê a Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Robin ainda está sob custódia deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:29.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Nami acabou de me atualizar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ouvi tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom... é isso que está acontecendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai lá e manda ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:43.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não seja imprudente, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Diga pra ele esperar até a gente chegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ei, cozinheiro! Está me ouvindo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tem uns caras malucos aí–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu disse que tá tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:52.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você faria se fosse você?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:02.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Depois de ouvir como a Robin mentiu\Ne foi presa pra nos salvar,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,você conseguiria ficar parado?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não adianta tentar pará-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você me conhece bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Cabeça de Alga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você está preocupado comigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:17.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cai na real, imbecil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:24.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,depois de ouvir como a Robin se sentiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mesmo que nosso capitão ordenasse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não tem como eu parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você quebrou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:37.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu queria perguntar algo ao Chapéu de Palha também!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Quem liga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deveria ter me avisado antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo sem avisar, não era óbvio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não seja tão arrogante!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não estou sendo arrogante.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que ele vai ficar bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dona! Faça o trem ir ainda mais rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais rápido?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:00.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É! Tipo, mais {\i1}vuuuush{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:08.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já ultrapassou o limite de velocidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:14.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e não consegue mais parar sozinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:22.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, enquanto eu estava fora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:25.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,tudo isso estava acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Robin não sabe sobre o {\i1}Merry{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:32.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,nem sobre a briga enorme entre você e o Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:41.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra que nós seis,\Nincluindo você, ficássemos seguros,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:46.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ela se sacrificou e obedeceu às ordens deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela fez isso por nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:55.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que história comovente!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que {\i1}você{\i0} está chorando?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu idiota! Não estou chorando!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:07.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Não acredito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:12.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Nico Robin era pra ser\Numa mulher cruel, selvagem, uma diaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:16.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas na realidade, ela tem\Num fraco pelos amigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Robin está logo ali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:22.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou resgatá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:23.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bem dito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sou o chefe da Família Franky, {\i1}o{\i0} Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:28.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou te dar uma mão, cara da sobrancelha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:33.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra ser sincero, tenho meus próprios motivos\Npra manter a Robin longe do governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:37.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E acima de tudo, quando ouço\Numa história tão emocionante...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:39.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Vamos, Narigudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:41.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:43.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não vou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já não tem mais nada a ver comigo, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:52.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se o próprio Governo Mundial\Nse tornar seu inimigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:54.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,eu não quero fazer parte disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:58.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você vai se juntar ao Luffy\Ne aos outros também, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:02.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Depois de toda a minha arrogância,\Ne depois de ter me humilhado,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:04.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,como eu poderia ficar ao lado de vocês?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:10.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito pela Robin,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:14.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas não tenho mais nenhuma obrigação\Nde ir salvá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:16.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu saí dos Piratas do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:23.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Falou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:28.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei! Como assim "falou"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:31.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não tem pra onde ir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:32.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixe ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:40.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que idiota teimoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.36,0:23:43.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vasculhem cada canto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:45.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ter alguma evidência em algum lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:47.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:48.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:52.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, se virem com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:58.21,Main-207+,,0,0,20,,{\q2}Wanze, senhor! O trem está em sérios problemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:23:59.33,Main-207+,,0,0,20,,Fiquem quietos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:01.80,Main-207+,,0,0,20,,Quem está em sérios problemas sou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nero, senhor! Os criminosos escaparam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Achei eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.07,0:24:25.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:27.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Metallic Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.49,0:24:36.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Quem está aí?!\N– Quem está aí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.63,0:24:45.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele me contou tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:48.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ouvi que vocês cavalheiros\Ndesejam resgatar uma donzela.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.26,0:24:52.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só isso já é motivo suficiente\Npara eu dar uma mão.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.26,0:24:55.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lutarei ao lado de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.02,0:25:03.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Podem me chamar de...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.36,0:25:06.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sogeking!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=17}===============================DIALOGUE============================
